      "message": "[Critical] Line 2004: Body-overwrite data is stored in one shared pluginData[\"bodyOverwrite\"] slot, but clearBodyOverwrites() is called for a single plugin and erases that shared slot from every affected message. If multiple chat plugins are enabled, unloading or changing one plugin can remove another plugin\u0027s overwrite, and updateMessageBodyOverwrite can overwrite another plugin\u0027s value. Namespace the cached overwrite by plugin identity or pass the plugin identity through Conversation so only that plugin\u0027s cached value is cleared/reloaded, then derive the displayed bodyOverwrite deterministically from enabled plugins.",
